title: Game.Exit
body:
Congratulations, you caught the killer.
<<exitGame MapObject>>

title: Game.Fail
body:
<<thinkingFont Dialogue>>  
Huh? My phone...
<<endThinkingFont Dialogue>>
->Answer
    Caller: Detective? This is the Station.
    Caller: We just got a report that Nora Hastings has fled the country.
    Detective: Dammit, where'd she go?
    Caller: North Korea.
    Detective: Whelp, we're not extraditing her from there.
    You have failed to catch the murderer.
    <<exitGame MapObject>>
